{
  "stem": "150.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Palestine said, we'll take them all.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There is no need for Jews to be refugees, to be sitting on foreign soil which is soaked in Jewish blood.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the British said, absolutely not.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So after there was no legal immigration, they had to resort to illegal immigration called Aliyah Bet.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they-- the Palestinians, the Israelis, tried to find whatever boats they could, whatever ships they could, and smuggled people into Palestine.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Most of them were caught by the British Navy, which was a very good Navy and very efficient.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Most of them were taken to the-- to Cypress, which was also a British colony, and put behind barbed wire with British soldiers at the gates.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when I got to Italy, the people there were being trained for Aliyah Bet, and also trained how to grow stuff and all that.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, and a very strange thing happened at the time, which took me a long, long time to understand.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were in this little agricultural settlement outside of the town of Magenta in Italy.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Everybody was very kind.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Everybody was nice.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There were mostly adults, about 70 or 80 adults.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there were about 10 or 12 kids my age, survivors from different camps.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we got along very nicely.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Then at one point the word came through that all the kids have to be transferred to another place, which is going to be a youth camp, a [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And so we went.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we got to this terrible place somewhere in the Italian Alps where it was raining all the time, and it was cold and miserable.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And there was just us and maybe 10 other kids from somewhere else.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And there was no adults.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There was a drunken Italian cook.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
